<TITLE>Jozef Karol Hell</TITLE>

<PARAGRAPH>
<REF ENTITY="0" MENTION="1" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np" SYNFUNC="subj" PREDICTION="plain_name" CHOICE="1">
<REFEX ENTITY="0" REG08-TYPE="name" CASE="plain" TAG="plain_name" NEW="yes">Jozef Karol Hell</REFEX>
</REF>
 (Slovak), Hell József Károly (Hungarian), Josef/ph Karl Hell (German) (1713-1789) was a mining engineer and inventor 
<REF ENTITY="0" MENTION="2" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np" SYNFUNC="subj_rel-clause" PREDICTION="nominative_pronoun_who" CHOICE="1">
<REFEX ENTITY="0" REG08-TYPE="pronoun" CASE="nominative" TAG="nominative_pronoun_who" NEW="yes">who</REFEX>
</REF>
, in 1755, invented the water-pillar, the world's first water pump machine. It is mainly used today for oil extraction. 
<REF ENTITY="0" MENTION="3" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np" SYNFUNC="subj" PREDICTION="nominative_pronoun_he" CHOICE="1">
<REFEX ENTITY="0" REG08-TYPE="pronoun" CASE="nominative" TAG="nominative_pronoun_he" NEW="yes">he</REFEX>
</REF>
 also proposed construction of the tajchy reservoirs around Banská Štiavnica. 
<REF ENTITY="0" MENTION="4" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np" SYNFUNC="subj" PREDICTION="nominative_pronoun_he" CHOICE="1">
<REFEX ENTITY="0" REG08-TYPE="pronoun" CASE="nominative" TAG="nominative_pronoun_he" NEW="yes">he</REFEX>
</REF>
 was a son of 
<REF ENTITY="1" MENTION="1" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np" SYNFUNC="obj" PREDICTION="plain_name" CHOICE="1">
<REFEX ENTITY="1" REG08-TYPE="name" CASE="plain" TAG="plain_name" NEW="yes">Maximilian Hell</REFEX>
</REF>
 and a student of 
<REF ENTITY="2" MENTION="1" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np" SYNFUNC="obj" PREDICTION="plain_name" CHOICE="1">
<REFEX ENTITY="2" REG08-TYPE="name" CASE="plain" TAG="plain_name" NEW="yes">Samuel Mikoviny</REFEX>
</REF>
.
